Wife, Mom, Youtuber & Vlogger

list.comment: I don’t love pumpkin spice lattes but I do love pumpkin spice makeup 😂🎃 This bronzey orange toned look is up now on my channel. All of the products I’m using are from @sephora ✨ To get direct links to everything make sure to download the @liketoknow.it app #ad #sephora #liketkit http://liketk.it/2xTgg

Is it just me or is a fresh new brush set the best?! 😍 You guys know @ecotools are my fave! This new set comes with 5 brushes, 50 blotting papers and the organizing tray! To celebrate the launch of this new limited edition set @ecotools is making a $100,000 donation to The Girl Project to help unlock the potential of girls everywhere 🙌🏽 #ad #ecotoolsXO #MyTrueBeauty
I can’t believe tomorrow is already his first Halloween 🎃He’s getting too big too fast! 😭 Sweater launches Sunday @shopgoodtobe

What’s everyone’s weekend plans? ✨ Were headed out to do a little shopping + pizza night! 🍕🍷 I know you guys loved this babydoll dress when I wore it last weekend. It’s the cutest little mini dress if you’re 5’4 and under- if you’re taller it looks amazing with leather leggings! This and so many other great pieces drop tomorrow on @shopgoodtobe at 11 am est!
My partner in crime- always going for the sweets! 😜
Nothing better than this ❤️ We’re so excited to start filming Vlogmas! What do you guys want to see this year? We have a couple trips/events planned! 🎄

Cozy days at home are the best. ❤️Especially now that we have Julian, I just love hanging out with him all day! I’ve been wearing a lot of casual outfits lately. This pink star sweater top is launching tomorrow with so many other cute items at @shopgoodtobe ✨ Joggers and other great sweats coming soon too!
Our new T-shirt line is live @shopgoodtobe 💞 We had so much fun working on this new line and this is just the start of what’s to come. Available in S-2xl and free shipping this weekend! ✨

A random photo @michael_maddalena took of me yesterday at our @shopgoodtobe photoshoot. Pretty much sums up my daily life at the moment- trying to balance mom life and work life. I had no idea what I was getting myself into by starting a new business and becoming a mom in the same year. But, I wouldn’t change it for the world and being a mom to Julian is the best thing that ever happened to me! Shoutout to all the moms just making it work everyday and having fun even on the long or hard days! 😘❤️

Fall days with the family 🍁 @michael_maddalena Outfit details: Julian’s coat is from H&M I bought it last year before he was born - so cute! Obsessed with these new Levi’s I bought yesterday bc it’s so hard to find high waisted jeans that actually fit right. Sweater is launching next Sunday on @shopgoodtobe

Fall weather is officially here in Michigan 🍁 What’s the weather like where you live? My cozy faux fur jacket launches this Sunday on @shopgoodtobe it’s so good- warm but lightweight and the color is 🔥

Such an honor to be on this months cover of @luxurluxmag 💞 You can pick up a digital or print copy now! It was so fun being able to share more about my entrepreneurial journey so far. Thanks to all of you for the continued support and love 😘 Cheers to all the girl bosses making moves! ✨
Baby giggles are the best 👼🏼✨

What is your go to moisturizer for dry winter skin? 💧 I need all the hydration! I started adding new products into my routine since using the Neutrogena Skin360™. If you haven’t already heard it is the coolest scanner that you connect onto your phone. You’re able to track your skin improvement it’s so fun seeing my skin change! #Seemyskin360 #ad #neutrogena_partner

Love my little family ❤️ New Video is up on our vlog channel. Come along with us on a couple @shopgoodtobe shoots and see a tour of our new offices! Also, sneak peek of @franceskax trying on wedding dresses.

I saw these for the first time last October and fell in love 😍 It took forever to find them in my size because I wanted to try them on before buying. I never splurge on heels anymore- only on things I can wear multiple times a week. I’m so excited to style these! ❤️ #louisvuitton #archlight
Officially in Christmas mode ❤️🎁 Can’t wait to decorate the tree when we get home from vacation! Soaking up the last few days of sun for now though ✨

HUGE NEWS! I’ve partnered with @ish to create my own palette the Natural Glow Face Palette ✨😭 #ishpartner
This has been a dream of mine since I started my channel. Thank YOU so much for following along and supporting me throughout the years. This palette is for all of you! ❤️ It’s the perfect palette for everyday to create that bronze glowy look that I love. The palette is available now on @shopgoodtobe and ish.com use code ALEX20 for 20% off the palette! #imsmokinghot

Loving my fresh hair thanks to @samglamm ✨ I just put up a chatty favorites video on my channel! Sharing the best high waisted jeans ever, a new skincare tool that I’m obsessed with and my current fave beauty and hair products! ❤️

Happy Sunday ☕️ Only a few more days til we leave for a little thanksgiving vacay and I cannot wait! What are your plans this year? ✨ This outfit and lots of other cute things launch today at 11 am est! @shopgoodtobe
Love these two ❤️ Even through teething Julian is always smiling, laughing and having fun! ✨
Pool days with this chunky monkey 🐵

Starting to get my gifts wrapped and ready for the holidays! ✨ This @ecotools Fan Favorites Beauty kit is the perfect gift for the makeup lover, it’s everything you need to highlight and contour. 💞 I love the pink color for the perfecting mini blenders! #ecotools #EcoToolsXo #ad 🎁

Now that it’s November the holidays are getting closer! ✨ Let’s hang out and wrap gifts together! 🎁 Check out my new video on the @ecotools channel for a sneak peek of the gifts I got for my friends and family this year including one of my favs the Warm Winter Glow set. #ad #ecotoolsxo
Happy Halloween from these 2 skeletons 🎃👻✨ Only 3 weeks apart and besties for life!
My little monkey 🐒😍❤️
Happy Halloween 👻🎃 What are your plans for tonight? Last year we had over 200 trick or treaters 😲 This outfit launches Sunday on @shopgoodtobe
My whole world ❤️
Baby bear 🐻 So excited for Julian’s first Christmas this year ✨

Thank you all so much for the support on the ISH x Alex Garza Natural Glow Palette! 😘❤️ I cannot wait for you all to receive your palettes in the beginning of December. It’d be a great item to add to your holiday wishlist 😉 Don’t forget the 20% off code ALEX20 ends tomorrow night on @shopgoodtobe

Our new T-shirt line drops on Black Friday, I’m so excited I cannot wait! I’ve been wearing everything in secret for weeks 😂 This moto jacket goes with everything and it’s available now @shopgoodtobe it’s the perfect closet staple.

We had such a fun week with our besties ❤️ Always make time for friends even when life gets crazy and hectic! It was so nice to relax, laugh and have fun this week. ✨ Both of these outfits drop at 11 am est tomorrow morning! @shopgoodtobe

Our new office is still pretty empty but at least we have our Christmas tree up! 😜 Where is your favorite place to shop for affordable furniture/decor? ✨ Don’t forget there’s a mini launch tomorrow with more bodysuits and sherpas (including the one in this pic) at 6pm EST on @shopgoodtobe

Walking into Monday like 😊✨ It’s a good week to have a good week! My biggest goal this week is to not overthink or make things harder then they have to be- I really need to keep things simple and enjoy everyday! ❤️ Btw loving this pink Sherpa from @shopgoodtobe it’s so warm and cozy!
Super baby! 😍 Michaels in FL working on our condo this weekend so it’s just the 3 of us 👶🏻🙎🏻‍♀️🐶 what kinda trouble are we going to get into?! I’m thinking some shopping with Grandma!
Date Night #OOTN from yesterday ❤️ I’m obsessed with this little baby doll mini dress coming soon to @shopgoodtobe it’s perfect with over the knee boots. These ones are @stuartweitzman ✨
